18.description:
Uanbai is a trading hub, that allows anyone to buy or sell anything on Twitter and Facebook with a "One Click" solution. Thus, sellers can benefit from their presence in Social Media and buyers can purchase without the hazzle of providing all their credit card information each time they buy something. 
The seller just need to go to www.uanbai.com and create an account, once done; he posts what he wants to buy and choose the social network where he would like to publish that. Once published, all their contacts in each social media can trigger a reservation by sharing, viralizing everything, afterwards they pay with Uanbai with our "one click" button and the sell is done!, then automatically the buyer dispatch the product or send an encoded mail for store pickup, given the case. 
Since the customer register his credit card in Unabai just the first time, his account allows him to buy with the same account to each seller that sells with Uanbai, and even pay bills.

Owners and top executives of a company, known as insiders, know better than anyone if the market valuation of their own company stock is

18.description:
Owners and top executives of a company, known as insiders, know better than anyone if the market valuation of their own company stock is the right one. There is evidence that, on average, when they acquire stock from their own company their profits outperform market averages. Thus, investors can make better investment decisions by following insiders’ movements.
Insiders Chile monitors in real-time and collects information on transactions made by insiders in the chilean stock market. Based on this information Insiders Chile generates real-time alerts, historical databases and statistics with value added for stocks investors. Clients of Insiders Chile have alerts services and access to databases and transaction statistics customized to user needs.

12.short_description: Bitrockr is a self-experimentation platform that enables users to track and analyze all their personal data on a central platform.

18.description:
bitrockr enables the user to track and aggregate data in one central platform by connecting a wide array of 3rd party devices or applications and also by inputting data directly into the platform using the web or mobile applications. bitrockr then using machine learning and statistical analysis, provides user with deep analysis and insights on various aspects of the users lifestyle. bitrockr also works as a secure personal data vault of the user by which the user can track their life and recall information when required. The user can also connect the platform with other products and services which require specific personal information to work.
The projected market size is very large as data has unlimited uses and utilization and with the increasing influx of new trackers and QS devices, users are bond to make use of the platform to gather maximum output from the data they generate using the trackers. Also, there is a rising trend in digital and external environments which provide services, catered to the user's personality and needs. Such platforms would connect to the bitrockr platform and gain access to specific data sets which define the user.
